毒<br />\n以前可以控制人去寫字去發命令<br />\n現代就用控制人用電腦程式發命令<br />\n有負面情緒就會病發 咁先有機會死<br />\n好似係咁上下<br />\n<br />\n其實原本唔合理求其話超自然力量咪算<br />\n兜太多扮科學反而仲垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e63ccd9ffe91adad4933160f6dac6c3cfc117d","tid":241264,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>國王遊戲真係好撚垃圾, 好後悔當年買咗書, <br />\n嗰陣睇到一半已經頂唔順, 不過不斷說服自己, <br />\n結局一定有得解嘅, 所以KEEP住買<br />\n<br />\n點知, 屌! 都唔係解晒嘅, 仲要再出下一季, 睬佢都傻<br />\n最後正式棄坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實最尾有冇解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有自我意識既新型病毒<br />\n以前可以控制人去寫字去發命令<br />\n現代就用控制人用電腦程式發命令<br />\n有負面情緒就會病發 咁先有機會死<br />\n好似係咁上下<br />\n<br />\n其實原本唔合理求其話超自然力量咪算<br />\n兜太多扮科學反而仲垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寫到邊諗到邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b55af378ba54a908160ab107b2fd131ded5e919","tid":241264,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:14:01.000Z","msg":"最垃圾係書局瘋狂推銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5288ec1640b0999563179bce719345822a1799","tid":241264,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:18:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最垃圾係書局瘋狂推銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中學雞好鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n哩套最死在人物描寫平面到已經唔記得有咩角色"}]}